Package com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport.factory

Contains factory classes for creating commands that are issued to the i2 Analyze command service.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CreateItemCommandFactory
    A factory for creating CreateEntity and CreateLink commands.
    LeaseCommandFactory
    A factory for creating ReleaseLease, TakeLeaseOnLatestItem, and TakeLeaseOnSpecificItem commands.
    ModifyItemCommandFactory
    A factory for creating AddCardToItem, AmendCardOnItem, AmendLink, DeleteCardFromItem, DeleteItem, and SetItemSecurityPermissions commands.
    SetCommandFactory
    A factory for creating AddLatestItemsToSet, AddSpecificItemsToSet, and RemoveItemsFromSet commands.

Package com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport.factory Description

Contains factory classes for creating commands that are issued to the i2 Analyze command service.
